parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electronic power steering system can cause the vehicle to lose power steering assist, making it difficult to steer, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The power steering assist fault message is displayed
the steering wheel is difficult to turn
the vehicle loses power steering functionality
the EPS warning light is illuminated
the steering wheel becomes firm or hard to turn
the vehicle pulls to one side.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel pump module can cause the engine to stall or prevent the vehicle from starting, increasing the risk of a crash.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or shuts down while driving
the vehicle will not start
the engine cranks but does not turn over
the fuel pump control module overheats
a strong odor of gasoline is present
the check engine light is illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The loss of fuel system pressure can cause the engine to stall or prevent the vehicle from starting, increasing the risk of a crash.
symptoms: The check engine light is illuminated
the vehicle stalls or shuts down while driving
the vehicle will not start
the fuel system pressure is low.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The presence of a gasoline odor and leaks can increase the risk of a fire or explosion.
symptoms: A strong odor of gasoline is present
gasoline leaks are visible or suspected.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the catalytic converter can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, increasing the risk of accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine light turns on
the vehicle stalls or loses power
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the water pump can cause the engine to overheat, leading to costly repairs or even engine failure.
symptoms: The vehicle overheats
coolant leaks
the water pump fails
the engine stalls or fails to start.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the throttle body can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, increasing the risk of accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
the check engine light turns on

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The stalling of the engine can cause the vehicle to lose power, increasing the risk of accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine stalls
